sentences.en: We cannot match warhead for warhead.
Ralph Langner, a German researcher, says Stuxnet has a “second warhead”.
sentences.cn: 德国研究者拉尔夫•兰纳(Ralph Langner)表示：该病毒还带有“第二枚弹头”。

sentences.en: It incorporates a steel case and penetrating blast-fragmentation warhead.
sentences.cn: 它集成了一个不锈钢表壳和穿透杀爆弹头。
